com.codename1.media
Class MediaManager

java.lang.Object
  com.codename1.media.MediaManager

public class MediaManager
extends Object

This class is the Media Manager creator. Media can be created with a String URI or with a stream of the media. Notice that the underlying platforms contains the actual codecs, therefore you need to play common media file types such as mp3, mp4 to succeed playing on all target platforms.

createMediaRecorder

public static Media createMediaRecorder(String path)
                                 throws IOException
Creates a Media recorder Object which will record from the device mic to a file in the given path. The output format will be amr-nb if supported by the platform.

Parameters:
path - a file path to where to store the recording, if the file does not exists it will be created.
